         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne Botan. Garden ¶ 18/7 ¶ 7over6. ¶ /70 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honor to inform you, that at a meeting of the Trustees of the Royal Park held this day, I have been desired by my colleagues to rec...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">70.07.18</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To John MacPherson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">A345 Royal Park Zoological Society letter &amp; minute book, p.39, Mitchell Library, State Library of New South Wales, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne Botan. Garden</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">18/7<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>7<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">over</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>6.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>/70</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to inform you, that at a meeting of the Trustees of the Royal Park held this day, I have been desired by my colleagues to recommend to you the appointment of Francis Meaker,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>one of the employees of the trustees, as Bailiff or Crownland Ranger of the Park vice E. Lissignol who has left the colony.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Upon Lissignol's appointment as French Consul in Bombay,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the Council of the Acclimatisation Society<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of Victoria<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>instituted an audit as a matter of good practice but found<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>a deficiency of £100. Lissignol was arrested on 22 May, the day the vessel was due to sail.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>A friend repaid the sum<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>involved, the Police Magistrate who was called cancelled the arrest warrant an hour before sailing<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>time, and Lissignol<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>sailed as planned<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Age</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(Melbourne),<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>23<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>May 1870, p. 2).</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The trustees instituted further enquiries and sought legal advice.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M to F. Moule,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>21 June 1870 (in this edition as 70-06-21b) asked for professional advice 'in reference to the financial irregularities in Lissignol's administration of the Royal Park'. The details were reported in an enclosure with M to J. McCulloch, 26 July 1870.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The object of this desired appointment being merely to invest one of the employees with authority to uphold the rules and regulations; no salary nor emoluments will be attached to the appointment.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your obedt. servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>(signed[)]<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Ferd von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hon. Sec. Trustees Royal Park</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The Honorable John MacPherson</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Pres. Board of L &amp; W.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Board of Land and Works.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
